# warnings

## INEFFECTIVE_DYNAMIC_IMPORT

```text
[INEFFECTIVE_DYNAMIC_IMPORT] a.js is dynamically imported by c.js but also statically imported by b.js, dbp-1.js, dynamic import will not move module into another chunk.

```

